00:02:11.460 --> 00:02:13.620
often used ineffective  lab tests of aggression.

00:02:13.620 --> 00:02:17.440
For example, measuring brain waves and heartbeats, which doesn't necessarily

00:02:17.440 --> 00:02:20.100
translate to actual criminal behavior.

00:02:20.100 --> 00:02:23.320
And in the past when a correlation has been found, it's been weak.

00:02:23.800 --> 00:02:26.860
Criminologists who study mass homicides refer to the link between

00:02:26.970 --> 00:02:29.200
violent games and crime as a myth.

00:02:29.200 --> 00:02:34.840
In fact in 2011 the US Supreme Court ruled that research did not find clear connection between

00:02:34.860 --> 00:02:37.200
violent videogames and aggressive behavior.

00:02:38.040 --> 00:02:41.060
Unfortunately, we all know how often after a crime,

